}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== Airlink+ rebranded to Airlink101.. and this switch line seems to have continued - see [[Airlink101 AGIGA5SW]] (UPC: 658729086104).
"Rev.A1" and "SOHO-GSW205T" is silkscreened on one the top of one AGIGA5SW - a date code of '''0347''' was found on the back. It's presumably a [[CAMEO]] product. :The same board is found [https://hisoap.azimech.net/others/etherHub/index.html on an Elecom switch at this reference (JP)].
A heatsink was attached (though, not too well) to the BCM2014 PHY.
